---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="border-t border-slc-grey/20 bg-slc-surface px-4 py-10 text-sm text-slc-text-muted">
	<div class="mx-auto flex max-w-5xl flex-col gap-6 md:flex-row md:items-start md:justify-between">
		<div>
			<a href="/" class="inline-block">
				<picture>
					<source
						srcset="/sousa-lima-consultoria-logo-horizontal-colorido.webp"
						type="image/webp"
					/>
					<img
						src="/sousa-lima-consultoria-logo-horizontal-colorido.png"
						alt="Sousa Lima Consultoria"
						class="h-7 w-auto max-w-[220px] object-contain object-left md:h-8"
						width="1000"
						height="334"
						loading="lazy"
						decoding="async"
					/>
				</picture>
			</a>
			<p class="mt-2 max-w-md">
				Conhecimento técnico a serviço da sua evolução.
			</p>
		</div>
		<div class="flex flex-col gap-2 md:text-right">
			<span class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-slc-grey">Legal</span>
			<a href="/politica-privacidade" class="transition hover:text-slc-navy">Política de privacidade</a>
			<a href="/cookies" class="transition hover:text-slc-navy">Política de cookies</a>
			<button
				type="button"
				id="slc-cookie-manage"
				class="min-h-11 text-left transition hover:text-slc-navy md:text-right"
			>
				Gerir preferências de cookies
			</button>
		</div>
	</div>
	<p class="mx-auto mt-8 max-w-5xl text-center text-xs text-slc-text-muted">
		© {year} Sousa Lima Consultoria
	</p>
</footer>
